      • fetchUncontrolledLoad

        public List<ConnectionMeterDataDto> fetchUncontrolledLoad(org.joda.time.LocalDate date,
                                                          int startPtuIndex,
                                                          int amountOfPtus,
                                                          List<String> congestionPointToConnectionAddresses)
        For each connection given as input, this method builds partially constructed ConnectionMeterDataDto which will contain PtuMeterDataDto with the uncontrolled load information for all the required ptus for each given connection.
        Parameters:
        date - LocalDate period.
        startPtuIndex - Integer index of the starting ptu.
        amountOfPtus - Integer amout of ptus (>= 1)
        congestionPointToConnectionAddresses - List of connection entity addresses.
        Returns:
        a List of ConnectionMeterDataDto.
